sqlInsert: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS users (     id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,     username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL UNIQUE,     password VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,     email VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL UNIQUE,     created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP )

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS devices (     id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,     user_id INT NOT NULL,     device_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,     device_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,     device_token VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL UNIQUE,     device_status ENUM('active', 'inactive') DEFAULT 'inactive',     device_setup_status ENUM('pending', 'completed') DEFAULT 'pending',     device_serial_number VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL UNIQUE,     created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,     FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE )
